"title": "6704: peace, divine in NT",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6704: peace, divine in nt",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's ultimate provision of peace is discovered in the person and work of Jesus Christ. It is only through Christ that peace with God can be achieved and maintained.</p>\n<h2>Provision of peace through the Father</h2>\n<h3>Peace in a believer's relationship with the Father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1\">ROM 5:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:1\">ROM 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:31-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:31–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:2-1Cor1:3\">1CO 1:2–1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Peace through the Father's provision for the believer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:25-Matt6:34\">MAT 6:25–6:34</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:22-Luke12:31\">LUK 12:22–12:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:7-Matt7:11\">MAT 7:7–7:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:9-Luke11:13\">LUK 11:9–11:13</a></p>\n<h2>Provision of peace through Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Through Jesus Christ's coming</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:10-Luke2:14\">LUK 2:10–2:14</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6-Isa9:7\">ISA 9:6–9:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:2-Mic5:5\">MIC 5:2–5:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9-Zech9:10\">ZEC 9:9–9:10</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:25-Luke2:32\">LUK 2:25–2:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:17\">EPH 2:17</a></p>\n<h3>Through Jesus Christ's teaching</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23-John14:27\">JHN 14:23–14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:3\">JHN 15:3</a></p>\n<h3>Through Jesus Christ's ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:36\">ACT 10:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:35-Mark4:41\">MRK 4:35–4:41</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:23-Matt8:27\">MAT 8:23–8:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:22-Luke8:25\">LUK 8:22–8:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:33-Luke4:35\">LUK 4:33–4:35</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:23-Mark1:25\">MRK 1:23–1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:38-Luke4:41\">LUK 4:38–4:41</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:14-Matt8:17\">MAT 8:14–8:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:29-Mark1:34\">MRK 1:29–1:34</a></p>\n<h3>Through Jesus Christ's death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:19-Col1:20\">COL 1:19–1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:5\">ISA 53:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:26-Matt26:28\">MAT 26:26–26:28</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:22-Mark14:24\">MRK 14:22–14:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:19-Luke22:20\">LUK 22:19–22:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:14-Gal6:16\">GAL 6:14–6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:13-Eph2:17\">EPH 2:13–2:17</a></p>\n<h3>Through Jesus Christ's resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:36\">LUK 24:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:4-Mark16:6\">MRK 16:4–16:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:1-Luke24:8\">LUK 24:1–24:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:19-John20:21\">JHN 20:19–20:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:26-John20:29\">JHN 20:26–20:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:14\">2CO 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:20-Heb13:21\">HEB 13:20–13:21</a></p>\n<h3>Through Jesus Christ's ascension</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:34\">ROM 8:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:51-Luke24:53\">LUK 24:51–24:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:33-Acts2:39\">ACT 2:33–2:39</a></p>\n<h2>Provision of peace through the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<h3>Through the Holy Spirit's inner witness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:21-2Cor1:22\">2CO 1:21–1:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:14-Rom8:17\">ROM 8:14–8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6-Gal4:7\">GAL 4:6–4:7</a></p>\n<h3>Through the Holy Spirit's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">ACT 9:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16-John14:18\">JHN 14:16–14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16-Gal5:18\">GAL 5:16–5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:17\">REV 22:17</a></p>\n<h3>Peace as the Holy Spirit's fruit and gift</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22\">GAL 5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:17\">ROM 14:17</a></p>",
